\MyProject\LolitaFramework\Core\Str::ascii
===

Transliterate a UTF-8 value to ASCII.

We use a simple phrase in greek and the ascii() method transforms every char in ascii.

Example usage
---
```php

$str = Str::ascii('Με λένε Μάριο!');

// Me lene Mario!
```

Parameters
---
_string_  __$value__

Return Value
---
__string__
